name: High Falls prototype
description:
this is a college project the controls are left and right arrows or a to go left and d to go right to move and mouse to click on any buttons

In order to play this game you will need to download this game file and extract all parts of the zip folder and double click the "New Unity Project.exe" to run the Game.

Once Completed you will need to press alt+F4 to close the game.
